section.para:
Once the user has installed the VMs they want to run on their computer and started them, switching between running VMs is as easy as using a keystroke (for example,
Ctrl+2
)or using the switcher bar, which appears when the user hovers the mouse in the middle of the top of the screen. Other than that, the user experience is almost precisely the same as running a single operating system.

